data.description: This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a gem! This property is situated in the desirable North Glendale area, close to parks, schools, shopping, and more.  NO HOA, RV GATE, RV PARKING, TOY FRIENDLY & SOLAR! Boasting brand new windows, beautiful pebble tec pool, and an open-concept kitchen and living room area, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. All appliances included!!!!! Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your new home!
